data.description: Enjoy the peaceful, serene and naturally beautiful setting with incredible mountain views on 3 acres in this custom built quality home. The backyard is parklike with pine and fir trees and giant granite boulders nestled between. Easy access to outdoor recreation, fishing, and hiking opportunities out your back door. The ideal Montana lifestyle awaits you with good internet service and an easy commute to Helena or Butte. This 5 bedroom, 2 bath home is well designed with lots of natural light, storage and gathering space. It has beautiful acacia wood floors, custom soft close cabinetry, stained concrete countertops and a cozy wood burning stove. An open floor plan connects the living/dining areas to a spacious kitchen with lots of cupboard space. A large woodblock countertop island allows for room to cook and entertain easily. Come see this dream home today!
